cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.HC, cs.GR, cs.CR

This paper analyzes player behavior in an MMORPG beta test, which falls under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI). The analysis also involves studying the impact of game mechanics on player behavior, which relates to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper uses data mining techniques to analyze the large dataset, which falls under the category of graphics (cs.GR) and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
